<hr local-id=3D"139734b6c578">
<h2 local-id=3D"73a19644b9f1" id=3D"PLATENG-I-25-Business/OperationalBenefi=
t(Score1=E2=80=935)">Business / Operational Benefit (Score 1=E2=80=935)</h2=
>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"db5228f8d27d" class=3D"conf=
luenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 190.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 190.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 148.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 231.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d9079fd6dd2c">
<th data-local-id=3D"55ccf3184005" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"33b6eb124624">Dimension</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"8d72ebf6984b" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"0d3acb702dce">Guiding Question</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"ecd8489faee5" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"84e1f31646c5">Score (1=E2=80=935)</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"c22b93dc058c" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"94deeb3f57a9">Rationale</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b62dbc648ff6">
<td data-local-id=3D"605804f3309c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2b91d65793db"><strong>Business Impact</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6de2c0992971" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4351467a1e43">Does this materially change outcomes, revenue,=
 or risk?</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3bf70ca90254" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dde69d8946bc"><strong>4</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dcdc2c733425" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bae3230a1dc8">Directly addresses a supply chain security ris=
k and is required by ESRO as the mandated tool of choice. Consolidating fro=
m multiple fragmented stores to a single managed repository. Materially red=
uces risk exposure. Particularly relevant given industry-wide increases in =
software supply chain attacks.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e69fa6263a86">
<td data-local-id=3D"b4c7bccc4912" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b71866fd142f"><strong>Operational Efficiency</strong></p></t=
d>
<td data-local-id=3D"aaafb385cb71" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"64fae62d28ce">Will this reduce toil, incidents, or manual ef=
fort?</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7f718581acb0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"24edda87ac7e"><strong>3</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"899d729b1856" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"021ae195b7c1">Eliminating the current mix of file shares, FS=
x, and S3 buckets as dependency stores will reduce the management overhead =
of maintaining multiple storage platforms and reduce the risk of inconsiste=
nt or stale dependency versions being consumed by pipelines.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"809282e70304">
<td data-local-id=3D"ddc584a176b8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c4bddb10848c"><strong>Time Sensitivity</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1540c9618670" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6edb997086a9">Is there a deadline, dependency or regulatory =
driver?</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b468c9aed0dc" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6fbcd05a11f7"><strong>3</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3f6701b01d36" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4bb1be5b0246">Driven by an ESRO mandate =E2=80=94 a complian=
ce/governance body, suggesting this is not optional. No specific deadline i=
s stated in the demand, but the directive nature of the requirement adds ur=
gency.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"bf8ab25b3f13">
<td data-local-id=3D"3504da7fa64a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5b9c9ee2eebd"><strong>Reuse / Strategic Value</strong></p></=
td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b7f00f84ba6a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"998c182e6d2b">Is this reusable across platforms or teams?</p=
></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"951fac1a9bf7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0168c727614b"><strong>4</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7c4ba7f80c73" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5a011f90e5cc">Artifactory is already listed as the Strategic=
 IaC tooling platform within EMIS/Optum. This change would benefit all team=
s consuming or publishing dependencies =E2=80=94 including Platform Enginee=
ring, CloudOps, Engineering, and any application team using IaC pipelines. =
The value compounds as adoption grows.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"0627e283bca4"><strong>Benefit Score: 14 / 20</strong></p>
<hr local-id=3D"f822986e0376">
<h2 local-id=3D"ed88871836a6" id=3D"PLATENG-I-25-Technical&amp;DeliveryComp=
lexity(Score1=E2=80=935)">Technical &amp; Delivery Complexity (Score 1=E2=
=80=935)</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"65608fe34c0e" class=3D"conf=
luenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 190.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 190.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 142.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 237.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"44934bcfde00">
<th data-local-id=3D"c71530614f56" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2ede047433fc">Dimension</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"79f7406d28db" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5d84c1a5dcca">Guiding Question</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f6a74446d73b" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"a32ec02717d5">Score (1=E2=80=935)</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"433f5376bb18" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"36bb67d5d8cc">Rationale</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5f9a17869491">
<td data-local-id=3D"c01861e666ed" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ce8aa5bf8a9b"><strong>Architectural Change</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"05c7f2323ce3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"35f3760d2c0d">New patterns, platforms, or core services?</p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a609ef272881" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"998138401c0c"><strong>3</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9e153e777ece" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c4ff6b9c60af">Artifactory is the approved strategic platform=
, so no new technology introduction is required. However, migrating from mu=
ltiple current storage locations (file shares, FSx, S3) to a centralised Ar=
tifactory instance is a meaningful architectural consolidation requiring de=
sign work for repository structure, access controls, and pipeline integrati=
on.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6038d66ebdf4">
<td data-local-id=3D"ae62a02b61dc" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ce11f7854a7f"><strong>Integration Complexity</strong></p></t=
d>
<td data-local-id=3D"59ba933b1ca3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7348634748a5">Number &amp; criticality of systems touched?</=
p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8b14011cde6f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b6a788b56610"><strong>3</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7bb95de1bccf" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"288501377f15">ADO pipelines, Terraform workflows, and potent=
ially application build/deployment pipelines will all need to be repointed.=
 The number of pipelines and teams affected is currently unknown =E2=80=94 =
this is a key risk that requires a dependency mapping exercise.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"598f2eac3352">
<td data-local-id=3D"ff7cf10e0b0b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1654244a28af"><strong>Security / Compliance Impact</strong><=
/p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7905828544bd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5edf7ff20e98">New threat models, controls, audits required?<=
/p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"406f024d2644" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c69c1f69c8d1"><strong>2</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3a759e95057a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"740339e253a5">The intent is to improve security posture (sup=
ply chain attack response). Implementing Artifactory as the single store re=
quires RBAC design, audit logging configuration, and integration with vulne=
rability scanning (e.g., Xray). These are established patterns within Artif=
actory and do not introduce novel security challenges.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6236a2f07b85">
<td data-local-id=3D"70256ceb5ce1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d48f996d359f"><strong>Operational Change</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"50a647e6b403" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"24ad5ce9417c">New runbooks, monitoring, on-call impact?</p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9f0c0593ae24" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"245870c653f7"><strong>2</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e303360adb9d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"69421cea61ff">Artifactory management runbooks will need to b=
e produced or updated. Monitoring coverage (Dynatrace / CloudWatch). Will n=
eed to be confirmed. This is manageable within normal operational onboardin=
g.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"b70a6827fd79"><strong>Complexity Score: 10 / 20</strong></p>
<hr local-id=3D"2175b750f0cf">
<h2 local-id=3D"3ac02c47f4ab" id=3D"PLATENG-I-25-EffortT-ShirtSizing(Archit=
ectureView)">Effort T-Shirt Sizing (Architecture View)</h2>
